OL,3,CKen Skates appointed as Welsh Labour's
OL,4,Cinterim leader
OL,6,FKen Skates has been appointed interim
OL,7,Fleader of Welsh Labour after Eluned
OL,8,FMorgan resigned on Friday (8 May)
OL,9,Ffollowing losing her seat in the
OL,10,FSenedd.
OL,12,FMr Skates will serve as leader until a
OL,13,Ftimetable is set for a full leadership
OL,14,Felection, the party said.
OL,16,FHe said: "Today is just the beginning
OL,17,Fof a process that will help us to
OL,18,Funderstand what we got wrong. Because
OL,19,Fwe did get it wrong.
OL,26,@xD@JOU
