OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778486754
OL,3,CKen Skates appointed as Welsh Labour's
OL,4,Cinterim leader
OL,6,F"There is no reading of this result
OL,7,Fthat endorses every action we have
OL,8,Ftaken as a party and our task now is
OL,9,Fto take the time needed and to work
OL,10,Fout what has happened.
OL,12,F"It is a task that will require every
OL,13,Fsingle one of us to take part in `
OL,14,Fevery member, every councillor, every
OL,15,FMS, MP, Lord and all roles in between.
OL,17,F"But it is not a task that is beyond
OL,18,Fus."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOUzD@DO]
