OL,3,CKen Skates appointed as Welsh Labour's
OL,4,Cinterim leader
OL,6,FMr Skates is the former Transport and
OL,7,FNorth Wales Secretary. On Friday, he
OL,8,Fsecured the sixth seat in the new
OL,9,Fconstituency of Fflint Wrecsam.
OL,11,FPaying tribute to Eluned Morgan he
OL,12,Fsaid: "I would like to thank Eluned
OL,13,Ffor everything she has done over the
OL,14,Fpast two years as our First Minister,
OL,15,Fand in her 30 years of service to
OL,16,FWales and the Labour Party.
OL,18,F"Her grit and determination in the
OL,19,Fface of true challenge is something we
OL,20,Fas a Party will always be proud of.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
