OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778486754
OL,3,CKen Skates appointed as Welsh Labour's
OL,4,Cinterim leader
OL,6,F"She broke the glass ceiling, and her
OL,7,Frole in history as the first woman to
OL,8,Flead our Party and country is an
OL,9,Fachievement second to none."
